<subSubSection pageId="10" pageNumber="411" type="etymology">
<paragraph blockId="10.[151,1437,151,794]" pageId="10" pageNumber="411">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,334,733,758]" pageId="10" pageNumber="411">Etymology.</emphasis>
The specific epithet is derived from the Latin “ 
<emphasis box="[861,900,733,757]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="411">sub</emphasis>
”, meaning under, and “ 
<taxonomicName box="[1164,1313,734,757]" class="Insecta" family="Tephritidae" genus="Acidiostigma" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="411" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="postsignatum">
<emphasis box="[1164,1313,734,757]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="411">postsignatum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
”, meaning 
<taxonomicName authority="Chen" authorityName="Chen" box="[151,400,769,794]" class="Insecta" family="Tephritidae" genus="Acidiostigma" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="411" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="postsignatum">
<emphasis box="[151,331,770,793]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="411">A. postsignatum</emphasis>
Chen
</taxonomicName>
, referring to the species’ similarity with 
<taxonomicName authority="Chen." authorityName="Chen." box="[854,1109,769,794]" class="Insecta" family="Tephritidae" genus="Acidiostigma" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="10" pageNumber="411" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="postsignatum">
<emphasis box="[854,1035,770,793]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="411">A. postsignatum</emphasis>
Chen.
</taxonomicName>
</paragraph>
